"""
test_dome_actions.py
--------------------
Comprehensive end-to-end test script for dome operations.
Covers status checks and physical movement tests with user confirmation
at each step. Always attempts to leave the dome closed at the end.

!! IMPORTANT: This script commands REAL hardware. Read each prompt carefully !!

Usage:
    python test_dome_actions.py

Configuration:
    Change TEST_DOME_KEY below to test a different dome.
    Key must match an entry in devices.yaml.

Location:
    testingcode/actions/test_dome_actions.py
    Run from within the actions/ folder or from testingcode/ folder.
"""

